    /// The input type of the operation to be conditionally applied.
    ///
    /// # See Also
    /// - Microsoft.Quantum.Canon.CControlled
    function CControlledA<'T> (op : ('T => Unit is Adj)) : ((Bool, 'T) => Unit is Adj)
